        <updateDate>2014-06-26T18:58:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Stop Penalizing Taxpayers for Sports Owner Fouls Act of 2014 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to deny to an individual who owns a professional sports franchise a tax deduction for any fine or similar penalty paid by such owner&nbsp;to the professional sports league or association. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
